OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright but
OL,6,Fpartly cloudy this evening. Risk of a
OL,7,Ffew showers for Argyll through the
OL,8,Fevening and night, while the Glasgow
OL,9,Farea will stay mostly dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA bright morning with hazy
OL,12,Fsunny spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,13,Fdevelop through the day and bring a
OL,14,Ffew showers, some of which may be on
OL,15,Fthe heavy side.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fwith a chance of showers or perhaps
OL,19,Fsome longer spells of rain on Friday
OL,20,Fand Saturday. Dry and brighter on
OL,21,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
